OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FSouth East Water must pay #30.5
OL,7,Fmillion after investigations by the
OL,8,Findustry watchdog following supply
OL,9,Finterruptions affecting hundreds of
OL,10,Fthousands of households across Kent
OL,11,Fand Sussex.
OL,13,FOfwat said the redress package
OL,14,Fconcludes three investigations into
OL,15,Fthe supplier and includes a previously
OL,16,Fproposed #22 million fine for water
OL,17,Fsupply failures between 2020 and 2023,
OL,18,Fwhich impacted more than 286,000
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
