OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FThe regulator launched a second probe
OL,7,Fat the start of this year after
OL,8,Ffurther supply interruptions in
OL,9,FTunbridge Wells and across Kent and
OL,10,FSussex between November and January,
OL,11,Fwhich left up to 70,000 homes without
OL,12,Fwater.
OL,14,FThe third investigation followed the
OL,15,Fdowngrading of South East Water's
OL,16,Fcredit rating by Moody's in May, which
OL,17,Fmeant the firm was in breach of its
OL,18,Flicence condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FAn independent monitor will be
OL,7,Fappointed by Ofwat to review South
OL,8,FEast Water's performance improvement
OL,9,Fplan and wider turnaround efforts.
OL,11,FSouth East Water will pay for the
OL,12,Findependent monitor, which is not
OL,13,Fincluded in the #30.5 million
OL,14,Fenforcement package.
OL,16,FHelen Campbell, executive director of
OL,17,Fdelivery at Ofwat, said: "South East
OL,18,FWater must now focus on what matters
OL,19,Fmost ` its customers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,F"These failures have caused real
OL,7,Fdisruption and hardship for residents
OL,8,Fand businesses across many years, and
OL,9,Fsupply interruptions of this scale
OL,10,Fhave happened far too often.
OL,12,F"This package is the first step
OL,13,Ftowards full accountability and to
OL,14,Fimproving overall performance, and we
OL,15,Fwelcome the company's engagement to
OL,16,Fbring these cases to a conclusion."
OL,18,FThousands of customers were left
OL,19,Funable to access tap water, shower or
OL,20,Fflush their toilets during the outages
OL,21,Fbetween November and January.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FSchools were closed and some customers
OL,7,Fhad to cancel work due to childcare
OL,8,Fissues as a result while others had
OL,9,Fdifficulty dealing with medical
OL,10,Fconditions, according to Ofwat.
OL,12,FThe watchdog found the company did not
OL,13,Fcommunicate "clearly and accurately"
OL,14,Fwith customers quickly enough and did
OL,15,Fnot provide those affected with
OL,16,Fadequate bottled water supplies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,F"The final #30.5 million package
OL,7,Freflects the full extent of failings
OL,8,Fidentified across the supply
OL,9,Fresilience and customer care
OL,10,Finvestigations and commits the company
OL,11,Fto fixing the problems identified,"
OL,12,FOfwat said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FThe redress package ` which must be
OL,7,Fpaid for by the firm's shareholders
OL,8,Fand not through customer bills ` will
OL,9,Finclude #5 million to provide free
OL,10,Fwater butts for households, #5 million
OL,11,Fto bring forward smart metering to
OL,12,Fbusinesses and other non-household
OL,13,Fcustomers, as well as a further #5
OL,14,Fmillion for on-site storage to help
OL,15,Fmanage their supply during peak demand.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FThe firm must also earmark #13 million
OL,7,Fof the package towards its turnaround
OL,8,Fplan, as well as #1 million for
OL,9,Fstorage and works at vulnerable sites
OL,10,Fwithin the area to boost supply
OL,11,Fresilience.
OL,13,FSouth East Water said in a statement:
OL,14,F"We are incredibly sorry for the
OL,15,Fhistorical supply disruptions that
OL,16,Faffected our customers across Kent and
OL,17,FSussex. We know this caused
OL,18,Fsignificant disruption and anxiety,
OL,19,Fand we accept the failures identified
OL,20,Fby Ofwat. It is not the standard of
OL,21,Fservice our customers deserve.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,F"Our priority has been to ensure that
OL,7,Fthe resolution of this investigation
OL,8,Fdirectly benefits those who suffered
OL,9,Fthe most. By working in collaboration
OL,10,Fwith Ofwat, we have agreed to a #30.5
OL,11,Fmillion redress package, which will be
OL,12,Fwholly funded by South East Water's
OL,13,Fshareholders. Choosing this route over
OL,14,Fa standard fine means these
OL,15,Fsignificant funds will directly
OL,16,Fbenefit those customers who were
OL,17,Fimpacted, some of them on multiple
OL,18,Foccasions."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784053121
OL,3,CSouth East Water to pay #30.5 million
OL,4,Cafter repeated supply failures
OL,6,FThe water company continued: "We are
OL,7,Ffully committed to learning from the
OL,8,Fpast, transforming our business and
OL,9,Fdelivering our largest-ever investment
OL,10,Fprogramme through our Price Review 24
OL,11,Fbusiness plan. We are focused on
OL,12,Fsustainably expanding our network
OL,13,Fresilience and drinking water storage
OL,14,Fcapacity so that we can prevent these
OL,15,Ffailures from happening again."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
